title: Are you tired yet?
author: VD
content_html: Dark Lord Designs and Cryptofashion have created what can only be described as a winning new design for sale. And yes, Trumpslide 2020 shirts are on the way. So much winning! It’s a nice way to soft-trigger those who inquire about what sort of winning is involved, at the wearer’s option.
